{"tid":121386,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【金正男遇害】金正恩肅清姑丈殺近千人 高射炮處決下屬","createTime":"2017-02-15T08:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T09:14:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98d45176b2cc21b3857abea60ab99b956f759e48","tid":121386,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T08:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170214/large/1487078768_0bb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170214%2Flarge%2F1487078768_0bb1.jpg&h=9c9d26c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓領袖金正恩自2011年上台以來，肅清異己絕不手軟，韓聯社近日引述脫北者指，金正恩單單對付政府前第二號人物、姑父張成澤的過程中，就屠殺了近1,000人，另20,000人受株連。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述南韓現任北韓戰略中心負責人姜哲煥稱，平壤政府肅清張成澤時，公開處決了415名執政勞動黨幹部、300多名黨屬機關幹部、200名人民保安省幹部，其中包括前領袖金日成的抗日游擊隊戰友家屬。另外，涉案人員家屬親人則被送入集中營，至少株連兩萬人。<br />\n金正恩的處決方式除了慣常的槍斃，亦有非一般的手段。軍方前第二號人物、人民武力部部長玄永哲，前年就疑因跟領袖金正恩頂嘴及出席官方活動時打盹，被冠上叛國罪名，當眾遭高射炮公開處決，反映金正恩求以「恐怖統治」鞏固威望。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170214/56305234\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170214%2F56305234&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmpnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=9967f62f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170214%2F56305234&h=3cce5232\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170214/56305234</a>"},{"pid":"d6f694e606aa994403d63e5c7a83e7120ba7e1f8","tid":121386,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T08:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2678de3e9dcadaa68439b46d6d